long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Ever land on website hosted on github.io, notice the URL and muddle the URL to try and find the repository? You're not alone!

Install this and you'll see a dancing Octocat on the top-right corner of pages you visit on the github.io domain. Click on it to view the source repository!

This extension will be used by literally tens of people worldwide.
